				<td colspan="2"><span>Can anyone give me tips on NToV, as in what would be the best role I should play? My guild is planning on going to NToV soon and it so happens that I am the only bard atm. So being the fact that I haven't been in a whole lot of raid type situations, much less NToV type situation with my bard, I was wanting any advice/input from you guys that may have been there before me. When I have raided with Evaal, I'm in the MT group and usually play my normal group setup, mix in resists if needed, and play AE mana during downtime. I'm pretty sure they are gonna want me in the MT group as usual so is there anything I need to know other than play the crap out of the resist songs right under the dragon's belly? As sad as it may seem thats the only thing I can think of to do. Any help will be much appreciated.</span></td>
