				<td colspan="2"><span>Well, here is my suggestion, best drum, resists, OOS, over haste, and katta's.  Katta's can be every other twist, making it easier.  The katta's will help a lot with making your MT group get lots of critical hits, with a good drum gives over 100 dex boost, plus the proc (and contrary to what I have read, the proc effects last for MUCH more than 18 seconds.  Two of my guildies dueled one night while we were all grouped, out of boredom, and I happened to have katta's playing at the time.  One of them took a proc hit, and the effects lasted for a couple of minutes... leaving him at 50 dex, lol.)</span></td>
